=== [[Riconnen's Challenge]] ===
The SatCom corporation is proud to present the latest and greatest in spectator warfare - Riconnen's Challenge.
Open to all able and willing warriors, the rules are simple. Survive.
Stand your ground in the Duel Ring against single opponents or dare to enter Sudden Death - Riconnen's ultimate challenge where you only get one chance to prove your worth.
Time your challenges carefully though for the first to win will reap all the benefits.
